params._newGreeting: (string memory) - new greeting to save on the contract

getAllBuilders().notice: Function to get all builders (addresses that have signed)

getTotalBuilders().notice: Function to get the total number of builders (unique signers)

hasAddressSigned(address).notice: Function to check if an address has signed the guestbook

setGreeting(string).notice: Function that allows anyone to change the state variable "greeting" of the contract and increase the counters

signGuestbook().notice: Function that allows users to sign the guestbook Each unique address adds a brick to the wall

withdraw().notice: Function that allows the owner to withdraw all the Ether in the contract The function can only be called by the owner of the contract as defined by the isOwner modifier

userdoc.notice: A smart contract that allows users to sign a guestbook and build a wall brick by brick
